node.text:
Delete, block, next.....remove toxic people from your life. Tag a friend that needs a reminder. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
You cannot hang with negative people and expect to live a positive life. 😮🤓⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Let go of the negative people in your life who are holding you back and weighing you down including close friends and family. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
People we need to leave behind. 👇🏼⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
1. The Debbie Downer⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Toxic people have a way of sucking the joy out of your good news and contorting your positive news into something negative. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
2. The Gaslighter⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Gaslighting is a psychological term that refers to one partner’s efforts to undermine the other’s grasp on reality in order to gain control. This is done by systematically making the victim feel like whatever the circumstances, her (or his) version of events is skewed, misconstrued, or imagined.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
3. The User⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
A user demands your time, energy and resources without taking your own wants and needs into consideration.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
4. The Friend You’ve Outgrown⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Friendships should be reciprocal and balanced. If they’re not, it may be time to move on.  Not everyone is meant to stay in your life.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
5.  The Critic⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Overly critical people often have low self-esteem and may be projecting their own insecurities onto the people around them.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
 So if a negative person is subtracting more than adding to your life, then make moves to distance yourself.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Hope this was helpful. Please share with a friend that needs a reminder. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Breath, Believe, Achieve ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

🚨 5 Step IG Growth Cycle🚨keep reading. ...

First thing first..... Are you on the waitlist? 🤩link in bio!

My Ultimate Instagram Blueprint is launching soon! 

It is a complete A through Z roadmap on building an audience of over 800k badass women entrepreneurs on Instagram organically and turning it into a cash-generating machine. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Now back to our 5 steps 😉
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Step 1️⃣ Pick your Niche/Industry
Identify your interest, passions, and skills. Determine the profitability of your niche. Build a community of people who are interested in what you are interested in. Then you start to see the power of Instagram. 
 
Step 2️⃣ Create 4-5 Content Pillars
Having content pillars will help you stay organized, consistent, and create high-quality content your audience will love.  Chose 4-5 topics your brand will consistently discuss and create content for on Instagram.  The more focused and niched you are in the beginning, the easier it will be to grow an audience of people who trust you.  Example: My content buckets for @womanceomindset are entrepreneurship, Mindset, women empowerment, Instagram growth, and monetization.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Step 3️⃣ Educate, Inspire and Entertain
Share educational content that delivers value to your audience like how-to videos, tutorials, charts, reviews, transformations, and tips.  Include Inspiration content such as quotes, before/after, and finally add some entertainment like memes and reels. 

Step 4️⃣ Position yourself as the expert in your field
Share content within your pillars. Provide value through education. Provide the solution to your audience's problems. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Step 5️⃣Create products that solve a specific problem 
What are your audience' pain points? What are they struggling with? Provide the solution to those problems with a product or service. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Which Step are you in right now? let me know in the comments😉👇🏼
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

Want my strategies to Building massive audiences on social? 

Get on the waitlist NOW! Link in bio 🔥
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.text:
Going through the motions leads to ordinary life. To be extraordinary, you have to push your limits every day.

Sometimes we get stuck going through life by simply going through the motions.

 We do just enough to get by. 

Until you realize that average effort isn’t enough if you want to win, to succeed, and to advance yourself.

To change your results, you must change your actions. You must leave your comfort zone.

👉🏼push yourself every day. 
👉🏼stretch your limits every day. 
👉🏼And surround yourself with people who are on a similar journey. 

Your circle should inspire you, push you to go harder, encourage you to follow your dreams, and give you strength when you're feeling down and unmotivated. 

If you feel like you need to level up your circle text me the word “CEO Circle” at 
+1 773-923-1411 and join the Woman CEO circle of women who want more out of life. Who are unapologetically ambitious and committed to pushing themselves to win at life.

If this sounds like you? .....join me. 

You will have direct access to me outside of Instagram land. 😊

I will be sharing money, business, mindset tips via text. 

My goal is to get your day started with the right MINDSET every morning so I will commit to texting you one of my favorite affirmations or inspirational quotes every morning. 

This way regardless if you are on IG or not I get to share my positive energy with you every day. 💫

Can't wait to see you on the other side. 

XO, 

Paula 💓

@womanceomindset
